322
00:16:15,370 --> 00:16:17,910
Much had happened between the time...

323
00:16:17,910 --> 00:16:19,910
of my workplace training and internship.

324
00:16:20,620 --> 00:16:22,500
He must be after more information,

325
00:16:22,500 --> 00:16:23,950
Hawks.

326
00:16:24,540 --> 00:16:26,700
Don't look down on me, the No.3 Hero..

327
00:16:26,700 --> 00:16:27,750
No.

328
00:16:27,750 --> 00:16:29,540
He's the No.2 Hero now.

329
00:16:30,830 --> 00:16:32,870
Tsukuyomi is so determined.

330
00:16:32,870 --> 00:16:34,450
He has a bright future ahead.

331
