338
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:08,750
I'd say 20% of my reason for choosing you
was because we're both birds,

339
00:17:08,750 --> 00:17:11,500
50% because I wanted to know more
about the League of Villains,

340
00:17:11,500 --> 00:17:17,829
