344
00:17:30,080 --> 00:17:33,660
It's a sound plan to strengthen your skill
in close-quarter combat.

345
00:17:33,660 --> 00:17:36,660
But never forget to develop
what you're already good at.

346
00:17:37,200 --> 00:17:39,700
You can move more freely.

347
00:17:41,040 --> 00:17:44,290
I never wanted to be a mentor.

348
00:17:44,290 --> 00:17:47,120
But since we're both birds,
I guess it must be fate.

349
00:17:51,370 --> 00:17:54,000
You belong in the sky if you can fly.

350
00:17:58,000 --> 00:18:01,370
Don't limit yourself to the ground.

351
00:18:04,540 --> 00:18:07,370
I will use the move I invented
when I worked with Hawks,

352
00:18:07,370 --> 00:18:09,830
Dark Fallen Angel.

353
00:18:10,660 --> 00:18:12,950
Dark Fallen Angel?

354
00:18:13,910 --> 00:18:15,620
That sounds fun,

355
00:18:15,620 --> 00:18:17,370
