357
00:18:21,750 --> 00:18:25,250
I'd never expected them
to launch a solo assault.

358
00:18:25,250 --> 00:18:27,870
It's the same situation as the first battle.

359
00:18:28,700 --> 00:18:30,410
It's time to improvise.

360
00:18:30,410 --> 00:18:33,580
